The mutation is: `case 3:` with no body, falling through to `case 4: return pull(read, ref[0], ref[1], ref[2], ref[3])`.

When `pull(f1, f2, f3)` is called, `length=3`, `args=[f1,f2,f3]`. The returned function gets `read`, then `ref=[f1,f2,f3]`.

